				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: How to keep from getting summoned?<a name="30203"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 24 04 12:36 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Depends on what you mean by &quot;too late.&quot;
<br />

<br />
It's too late if you want to avoid being summoned ever.
<br />

<br />
It's not too late if one summon doesn't spell your doom.  
<br />

<br />
But when the message appears on your screen:  &quot;Sontalak says &quot;You will not evade me, Irena!&quot;&quot;, then you done been summoned.  You are now up close and snuggly with Sontalak.
<br />

<br />
What you choose to do in that situation is your own lookout.</span></td>
