				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: How to keep from getting summoned?<a name="31984"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 31 04 1:35 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Not gonna work.  Summoning works like this.  Once the mob has taken a certain amount of damage, it will begin summoning and will summon at regular intervals.  It always summons whoever is at the top of its hate list.
<br />

<br />
So, either you're on the hate list or you're not.
<br />

<br />
If you are, it'll summon you.
<br />
If you're not, it won't.
<br />

<br />
Now, if you're not on the hate list, why is the mob hitting you and provoking your pet into defending?</span></td>
